  "body": "Given that has many contributors with different styling preferences, CI should ensure a more cohesive style.\r\n\r\n**Examples**\r\n\r\nFrom https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/3205 use of single or double quotes in YAML\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/e8ce723abc5014b810a5b30c4e14aa6eebdad043/configs/mainnet.yaml#L3-L4\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/84fcfa8b2fda2452ccd1e18d94f12f9bb526ab7c/configs/mainnet.yaml#L3-L4\r\n\r\nFrom `specs/_features/sharding/beacon-chain.md`. Spaced out container declaration vs non spaced out. Field comments on same line vs on previous line \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/84fcfa8b2fda2452ccd1e18d94f12f9bb526ab7c/specs/_features/sharding/beacon-chain.md?plain=1#L119-L127\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/84fcfa8b2fda2452ccd1e18d94f12f9bb526ab7c/specs/_features/sharding/beacon-chain.md?plain=1#L143-L145\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/84fcfa8b2fda2452ccd1e18d94f12f9bb526ab7c/specs/_features/sharding/beacon-chain.md?plain=1#L151-L155\r\n\r\nWhile pedantic, this is common in most languages default tooling and exist in most implementation codebases",
